{"tid":423224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廉署立案查何君堯涉虛報執業資格 疑違選舉失實陳述","createTime":"2017-10-03T17:14:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T18:20:34.000Z","uid":36494,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4358afa1d7bb889a1452a0540ccfc7c735f40394","tid":423224,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T17:14:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171004&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57288267\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171004%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57288267&d=4Ce4bwXm6I27l%2B5pQKYRApZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=924ea783\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171004%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57288267&h=02554632\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171004&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57288267</a><br />\n廉署立案查何君堯涉虛報執業資格 疑違選舉失實陳述<br />\n<br />\n新民主同盟上月25日向廉署舉報立法會議員何君堯，稱何在選舉通函聲稱自己為「英國執業律師」，與事實不符，涉觸犯《選舉（舞弊及非法行為）條例》，促請廉署徹查。據了解，廉署已決定立案調查。廉署發言人回應傳媒查詢時指，根據政策，廉署一般不評論個別案件。<br />\n<br />\n新同盟范國威上周報案前指，何君堯去年參選立法會時在選舉通函上聲稱自己是「英國執業律師」，是與事實不符，而何君堯在律師樓網頁修改其個人簡介，足以證明他早前提供的資料不真確。"},{"pid":"31cad28f12ab392e8a9f105a9b089f4586797b28","tid":423224,"uid":69930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T17:30:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b009bd613fc94d7cc40bf220187d74705b04742d","tid":423224,"uid":12755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T18:07:24.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"824357323b1483b424bd97669656fe5d5ae6e13a","tid":423224,"uid":37874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T18:16:09.000Z","msg":"連續幾次宣傳都用執業律師<br />\n如果咁都無事 廉署不如解散左佢算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc4bd36982741eb1a1c113c12ffd8ca6f03be5b","tid":423224,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T18:20:34.000Z","msg":"推到佢坐監"}]}